{"tid":1822700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"影大頭到底有咩問題","createTime":"2020-01-13T06:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T20:04:17.000Z","uid":198394,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5da122c6722325b50dda29ba70aabd6900424c54","tid":1822700,"uid":198394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:19:18.000Z","msg":"事實上<br />\n好矛盾<br />\n因為<br />\n你影人嗰下<br />\n根本分唔到<br />\n邊D係手足<br />\n邊D係blue C <br />\n如果手足真係有經濟困難<br />\n然後去食美心<br />\n咁就比你影左<br />\n咁點算<br />\nOr <br />\n我地標準係以食唔食黃店判斷佢係咪真黃？<br />\n但係同時影相的確可以施壓<br />\n同埋如果你話係批鬥藍C，咁又點呀？<br />\n佢地絕對deserve it <br />\n但係以最保守嚟計，唔影似乎好D？<br />\n以下開放討論"},{"pid":"1aaedde2267b1d40daf2e7a765a9cacf4ea47c1c","tid":1822700,"uid":198394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:19:24.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"b9e0284d44b27f0a845227689e8e23e1fe262ef4","tid":1822700,"uid":198394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:19:37.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"6c416118ac3dc40c17b074b4780af6a62975e1b4","tid":1822700,"uid":198394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:19:50.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"8cf70e4149fcd5fc86caaaf8bdc2d6454648a343","tid":1822700,"uid":228143,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:20:07.000Z","msg":"和你影係用來迫中立既人表態<br />\n<br />\n同中美對台大選一樣<br />\n<br />\n只可以簡一邊冇中立空間<br />\n<br />\n結果先會有大勝<br />\n<br />\n區選贏硬居然話失民意<br />\n<br />\n如果你見到你上司/同事係藍/港豬<br />\n<br />\n你都會改觀<br />\n<br />\n和你影係加速對立面<br />\n<br />\n好唔好你睇台選就知  以後冇中立嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n其實中立即係等死 都膠嫁啦"},{"pid":"09b64ce28986ed3e363dfa0a73334be53e36eb96","tid":1822700,"uid":60563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:20:44.000Z","msg":"m記你都講得通<br />\n食美心係窮手足???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor